'''Steven Allen Rosenberg''' (born October 31, 1964 in [[Brooklyn, New York|Brooklyn]], [[New York]]) is an [[United States|American]] former left-handed [[starting pitcher]] in [[Major League Baseball]]. He played for the [[Chicago White Sox]] (1988-90) and the [[San Diego Padres]] (1991). <ref>[http://www.baseball-reference.com/r/rosenst01.shtml baseball-reference.com]</ref>

